{
  "video_id": "6liIKYeUzaY",
  "title": "Everything you hear on film is a lie | Tasos Frantzolas",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12952.0,
      "end_time": 16857.0,
      "text": "I want to start by doing an experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16857.0,
      "end_time": 20935.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to play three videos of a rainy day."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20935.0,
      "end_time": 24843.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;ve replaced the audio of one of the videos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24843.0,
      "end_time": 27241.0,
      "text": "and instead of the sound of rain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27241.0,
      "end_time": 31137.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve added the sound of bacon frying."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31137.0,
      "end_time": 35695.0,
      "text": "So I want you think carefully which one the clip with the bacon is."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35695.0,
      "end_time": 39394.0,
      "text": "(Rain falls)"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39394.0,
      "end_time": 43627.0,
      "text": "(Rain falls)"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 43627.0,
      "end_time": 52611.0,
      "text": "(Rain falls)"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 52611.0,
      "end_time": 55064.0,
      "text": "All right."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 55064.0,
      "end_time": 57662.0,
      "text": "Actually, I lied."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 57662.0,
      "end_time": 58956.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re all bacon."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 58956.0,
      "end_time": 64276.0,
      "text": "(Bacon sizzles)"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 64275.99999999999,
      "end_time": 69216.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 69216.0,
      "end_time": 72513.0,
      "text": "My point here isn&#39;t really to make you hungry"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 72513.0,
      "end_time": 74186.0,
      "text": "every time you see a rainy scene,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 74186.0,
      "end_time": 80696.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s to show that our brains are conditioned to embrace the lies."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 80696.0,
      "end_time": 83754.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not looking for accuracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 83754.0,
      "end_time": 86563.0,
      "text": "So on the subject of deception,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 86563.0,
      "end_time": 89950.0,
      "text": "I wanted to quote one of my favorite authors."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 89950.0,
      "end_time": 96923.0,
      "text": "In &quot;The Decay of Lying,&quot; Oscar Wilde establishes the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 96923.0,
      "end_time": 103096.0,
      "text": "that all bad art comes from copying nature and being realistic;"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 103096.0,
      "end_time": 109030.0,
      "text": "and all great art comes from lying and deceiving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 109030.0,
      "end_time": 112087.0,
      "text": "and telling beautiful, untrue things."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 112087.0,
      "end_time": 116890.0,
      "text": "So when you&#39;re watching a movie"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 116890.0,
      "end_time": 118426.0,
      "text": "and a phone rings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 118426.0,
      "end_time": 120942.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not actually ringing."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 120942.0,
      "end_time": 125220.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s been added later in postproduction in a studio."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 125220.0,
      "end_time": 128098.0,
      "text": "All of the sounds you hear are fake."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 128098.00000000001,
      "end_time": 129932.00000000001,
      "text": "Everything, apart from the dialogue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 129931.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131110.0,
      "text": "is fake."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 131110.0,
      "end_time": 134794.0,
      "text": "When you watch a movie and you see a bird flapping its wings --"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 134794.0,
      "end_time": 138141.0,
      "text": "(Wings flap)"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 138141.0,
      "end_time": 140428.0,
      "text": "They haven&#39;t really recorded the bird."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 140428.0,
      "end_time": 145446.0,
      "text": "It sounds a lot more realistic if you record a sheet"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 145446.0,
      "end_time": 147022.0,
      "text": "or shaking kitchen gloves."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 147022.0,
      "end_time": 150849.0,
      "text": "(Flaps)"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 150849.0,
      "end_time": 153816.0,
      "text": "The burning of a cigarette up close --"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 153816.0,
      "end_time": 157351.0,
      "text": "(Cigarette burns)"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 157351.0,
      "end_time": 160126.0,
      "text": "It actually sounds a lot more authentic"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 160126.0,
      "end_time": 162995.0,
      "text": "if you take a small Saran Wrap ball"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 162995.0,
      "end_time": 164237.0,
      "text": "and release it."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 164237.0,
      "end_time": 167869.0,
      "text": "(A Saran Warp ball being released)"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 167869.0,
      "end_time": 169296.0,
      "text": "Punches?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 169296.0,
      "end_time": 170842.0,
      "text": "(Punch)"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 170842.0,
      "end_time": 172798.0,
      "text": "Oops, let me play that again."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 172798.0,
      "end_time": 174535.0,
      "text": "(Punch)"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 174535.0,
      "end_time": 178295.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s often done by sticking a knife in vegetables,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 178295.0,
      "end_time": 180661.0,
      "text": "usually cabbage."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 180661.0,
      "end_time": 182788.0,
      "text": "(Cabbage stabbed with a knife)"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 182788.0,
      "end_time": 185776.0,
      "text": "The next one -- it&#39;s breaking bones."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 185776.0,
      "end_time": 188670.0,
      "text": "(Bones break)"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 188670.0,
      "end_time": 191028.0,
      "text": "Well, no one was really harmed."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 191028.0,
      "end_time": 193163.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s actually ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 193163.0,
      "end_time": 196442.0,
      "text": "breaking celery or frozen lettuce."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 196442.0,
      "end_time": 198947.0,
      "text": "(Breaking frozen lettuce or celery)"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 198947.0,
      "end_time": 201253.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 201253.0,
      "end_time": 205992.0,
      "text": "Making the right sounds is not always as easy"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 205992.0,
      "end_time": 207923.0,
      "text": "as a trip to the supermarket"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 207923.0,
      "end_time": 210643.0,
      "text": "and going to the vegetable section."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 210643.0,
      "end_time": 213042.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s often a lot more complicated than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 213042.0,
      "end_time": 216089.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s reverse-engineer together"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 216089.0,
      "end_time": 218437.0,
      "text": "the creation of a sound effect."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 218437.0,
      "end_time": 221810.0,
      "text": "One of my favorite stories comes from Frank Serafine."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 221810.0,
      "end_time": 223685.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s a contributor to our library,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 223685.0,
      "end_time": 228291.0,
      "text": "and a great sound designer for &quot;Tron&quot; and &quot;Star Trek&quot; and others."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 228291.0,
      "end_time": 233573.0,
      "text": "He was part of the Paramount team that won the Oscar for best sound"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 233573.0,
      "end_time": 235528.0,
      "text": "for &quot;The Hunt for Red October.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 235528.0,
      "end_time": 238942.0,
      "text": "In this Cold War classic, in the &#39;90s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 238942.0,
      "end_time": 243751.0,
      "text": "they were asked to produce the sound of the propeller of the submarine."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 243751.0,
      "end_time": 245120.0,
      "text": "So they had a small problem:"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 245120.0,
      "end_time": 248664.0,
      "text": "they couldn&#39;t really find a submarine in West Hollywood."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 248664.0,
      "end_time": 252346.0,
      "text": "So basically, what they did is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 252346.0,
      "end_time": 255725.0,
      "text": "they went to a friend&#39;s swimming pool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 255725.0,
      "end_time": 261069.0,
      "text": "and Frank performed a cannonball, or bomba."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 261069.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263289.0,
      "text": "They placed an underwater mic"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 263289.0,
      "end_time": 266089.0,
      "text": "and an overhead mic outside the swimming pool."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 266089.0,
      "end_time": 269366.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s what the underwater mic sounds like."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 269366.0,
      "end_time": 271608.0,
      "text": "(Underwater plunge)"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 271608.0,
      "end_time": 273138.0,
      "text": "Adding the overhead mic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 273138.0,
      "end_time": 275115.0,
      "text": "it sounded a bit like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 275115.0,
      "end_time": 277514.0,
      "text": "(Water splashes)"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 277514.0,
      "end_time": 281985.0,
      "text": "So now they took the sound and pitched it one octave down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 281985.0,
      "end_time": 284850.0,
      "text": "sort of like slowing down a record."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 284850.0,
      "end_time": 287929.0,
      "text": "(Water splashes at lower octave)"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 287929.0,
      "end_time": 290721.0,
      "text": "And then they removed a lot of the high frequencies."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 290721.0,
      "end_time": 293020.0,
      "text": "(Water splashes)"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 293020.0,
      "end_time": 296314.0,
      "text": "And pitched it down another octave."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 296314.0,
      "end_time": 298626.0,
      "text": "(Water splashes at lower octave)"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 298626.0,
      "end_time": 301156.0,
      "text": "And then they added a little bit of the splash"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 301156.0,
      "end_time": 303464.0,
      "text": "from the overhead microphone."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 303464.0,
      "end_time": 306653.0,
      "text": "(Water splashes)"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 306653.0,
      "end_time": 309215.0,
      "text": "And by looping and repeating that sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 309215.0,
      "end_time": 310429.0,
      "text": "they got this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 310429.0,
      "end_time": 316463.0,
      "text": "(Propeller churns)"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 316463.0,
      "end_time": 323015.0,
      "text": "So, creativity and technology put together in order to create the illusion"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 323015.0,
      "end_time": 326868.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re inside the submarine."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 326868.0,
      "end_time": 330253.0,
      "text": "But once you&#39;ve created your sounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 330253.0,
      "end_time": 332671.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;ve synced them to the image,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 332671.0,
      "end_time": 337397.0,
      "text": "you want those sounds to live in the world of the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 337397.0,
      "end_time": 341997.0,
      "text": "And one the best ways to do that is to add reverb."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 341997.0,
      "end_time": 345198.0,
      "text": "So this is the first audio tool I want to talk about."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 345198.0,
      "end_time": 350344.0,
      "text": "Reverberation, or reverb, is the persistence of the sound"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 350344.0,
      "end_time": 352299.0,
      "text": "after the original sound has ended."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 352299.0,
      "end_time": 354891.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s sort of like the --"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 354891.0,
      "end_time": 357951.0,
      "text": "all the reflections from the materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 357951.0,
      "end_time": 360862.0,
      "text": "the objects and the walls around the sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 360862.0,
      "end_time": 363098.0,
      "text": "Take, for example, the sound of a gunshot."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 363098.0,
      "end_time": 368138.0,
      "text": "The original sound is less than half a second long."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 368138.0,
      "end_time": 369747.0,
      "text": "(Gunshot)"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 369747.0,
      "end_time": 371460.0,
      "text": "By adding reverb,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 371460.0,
      "end_time": 375470.0,
      "text": "we can make it sound like it was recorded inside a bathroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 375470.0,
      "end_time": 377057.0,
      "text": "(Gunshot reverbs in bathroom)"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 377057.0,
      "end_time": 380887.0,
      "text": "Or like it was recorded inside a chapel or a church."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 380887.0,
      "end_time": 383043.0,
      "text": "(Gunshot reverbs church)"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 383043.0,
      "end_time": 386199.0,
      "text": "Or in a canyon."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 386199.0,
      "end_time": 387984.0,
      "text": "(Gunshot reverbs in canyon)"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 387984.0,
      "end_time": 390661.0,
      "text": "So reverb gives us a lot of information"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 390661.0,
      "end_time": 395615.0,
      "text": "about the space between the listener and the original sound source."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 395615.0,
      "end_time": 397748.0,
      "text": "If the sound is the taste,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 397748.0,
      "end_time": 402309.0,
      "text": "then reverb is sort of like the smell of the sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 402309.0,
      "end_time": 404491.0,
      "text": "But reverb can do a lot more."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 404491.0,
      "end_time": 408425.0,
      "text": "Listening to a sound with a lot less reverberation"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 408425.0,
      "end_time": 410532.0,
      "text": "than the on-screen action"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 410532.0,
      "end_time": 413576.0,
      "text": "is going to immediately signify to us"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 413576.0,
      "end_time": 416243.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re listening to a commentator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 416243.0,
      "end_time": 422471.0,
      "text": "to an objective narrator that&#39;s not participating in the on-screen action."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 422471.0,
      "end_time": 426686.0,
      "text": "Also, emotionally intimate moments in cinema"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 426686.0,
      "end_time": 428657.0,
      "text": "are often heard with zero reverb,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 428657.0,
      "end_time": 433024.0,
      "text": "because that&#39;s how it would sound if someone was speaking inside our ear."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 433024.0,
      "end_time": 435009.0,
      "text": "On the completely other side,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 435009.0,
      "end_time": 437529.0,
      "text": "adding a lot of reverb to a voice"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 437529.0,
      "end_time": 441637.0,
      "text": "is going to make us think that we&#39;re listening to a flashback,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 441637.0,
      "end_time": 445946.0,
      "text": "or perhaps that we&#39;re inside the head of a character"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 445946.0,
      "end_time": 448446.0,
      "text": "or that we&#39;re listening to the voice of God."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 448446.0,
      "end_time": 450732.0,
      "text": "Or, even more powerful in film,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 450732.0,
      "end_time": 452243.0,
      "text": "Morgan Freeman."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 452243.0,
      "end_time": 453551.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 453551.0,
      "end_time": 454742.0,
      "text": "So --"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 454742.0,
      "end_time": 457502.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 457502.0,
      "end_time": 461397.0,
      "text": "But what are some other tools or hacks"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 461397.0,
      "end_time": 464186.0,
      "text": "that sound designers use?"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 464186.0,
      "end_time": 471901.0,
      "text": "Well, here&#39;s a really big one."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 471901.0,
      "end_time": 473807.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 473807.0,
      "end_time": 477881.0,
      "text": "A few moments of silence is going to make us pay attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 477881.0,
      "end_time": 480345.0,
      "text": "And in the Western world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 480345.0,
      "end_time": 482492.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re not really used to verbal silences."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 482492.0,
      "end_time": 486537.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re considered awkward or rude."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 486537.0,
      "end_time": 491021.0,
      "text": "So silence preceding verbal communication"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 491021.0,
      "end_time": 493105.0,
      "text": "can create a lot of tension."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 493105.0,
      "end_time": 496834.0,
      "text": "But imagine a really big Hollywood movie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 496834.0,
      "end_time": 502389.0,
      "text": "where it&#39;s full of explosions and automatic guns."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 502389.0,
      "end_time": 506008.0,
      "text": "Loud stops being loud anymore, after a while."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 506008.0,
      "end_time": 507976.0,
      "text": "So in a yin-yang way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 507976.0,
      "end_time": 511137.0,
      "text": "silence needs loudness and loudness needs silence"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 511137.0,
      "end_time": 514350.0,
      "text": "for either of them to have any effect."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 514350.0,
      "end_time": 515751.0,
      "text": "But what does silence mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 515751.0,
      "end_time": 519416.0,
      "text": "Well, it depends how it&#39;s used in each film."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 519416.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522619.00000000006,
      "text": "Silence can place us inside the head of a character"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 522619.0,
      "end_time": 524261.0,
      "text": "or provoke thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 524260.99999999994,
      "end_time": 528654.0,
      "text": "We often relate silences with ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 528654.0,
      "end_time": 530558.0,
      "text": "contemplation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 530558.0,
      "end_time": 533185.0,
      "text": "meditation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 533185.0,
      "end_time": 536569.0,
      "text": "being deep in thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 536569.0,
      "end_time": 539695.0,
      "text": "But apart from having one meaning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 539695.0,
      "end_time": 541889.0,
      "text": "silence becomes a blank canvas"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 541889.0,
      "end_time": 546962.0,
      "text": "upon which the viewer is invited to the paint their own thoughts."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 546962.0,
      "end_time": 551192.0,
      "text": "But I want to make it clear: there is no such thing as silence."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 551192.0,
      "end_time": 556835.0,
      "text": "And I know this sounds like the most pretentious TED Talk statement ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 556835.0,
      "end_time": 562164.0,
      "text": "But even if you were to enter a room with zero reverberation"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 562164.0,
      "end_time": 564253.0,
      "text": "and zero external sounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 564253.0,
      "end_time": 568004.0,
      "text": "you would still be able to hear the pumping of your own blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 568004.0,
      "end_time": 572345.0,
      "text": "And in cinema, traditionally, there was never a silent moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 572345.0,
      "end_time": 574716.0,
      "text": "because of the sound of the projector."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 574716.0,
      "end_time": 578034.0,
      "text": "And even in today&#39;s Dolby world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 578034.0,
      "end_time": 582485.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s not really any moment of silence if you listen around you."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 582485.0,
      "end_time": 584734.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s always some sort of noise."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 584734.0,
      "end_time": 587685.0,
      "text": "Now, since there&#39;s no such thing as silence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 587685.0,
      "end_time": 591280.0,
      "text": "what do filmmakers and sound designers use?"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 591280.0,
      "end_time": 596307.0,
      "text": "Well, as a synonym, they often use ambiences."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 596307.0,
      "end_time": 600200.0,
      "text": "Ambiences are the unique background sounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 600200.0,
      "end_time": 603272.0,
      "text": "that are specific to each location."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 603272.0,
      "end_time": 605145.0,
      "text": "Each location has a unique sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 605145.0,
      "end_time": 607145.0,
      "text": "and each room has a unique sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 607145.0,
      "end_time": 608742.0,
      "text": "which is called room tone."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 608742.0,
      "end_time": 611189.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s a recording of a market in Morocco."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 611189.0,
      "end_time": 617470.0,
      "text": "(Voices, music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 617470.0,
      "end_time": 620843.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s a recording of Times Square in New York."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 620843.0,
      "end_time": 627449.0,
      "text": "(Traffic sounds, car horns, voices)"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 627449.0,
      "end_time": 631095.0,
      "text": "Room tone is the addition of all the noises inside the room:"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 631095.0,
      "end_time": 633508.0,
      "text": "the ventilation, the heating, the fridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 633508.0,
      "end_time": 636443.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a recording of my apartment in Brooklyn."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 636443.0,
      "end_time": 647422.0,
      "text": "(You can hear the ventilation, the boiler, the fridge and street traffic)"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 647422.0,
      "end_time": 652718.0,
      "text": "Ambiences work in a most primal way."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 652718.0,
      "end_time": 656538.0,
      "text": "They can speak directly to our brain subconsciously."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 656538.0,
      "end_time": 662937.0,
      "text": "So, birds chirping outside your window may indicate normality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 662937.0,
      "end_time": 665752.0,
      "text": "perhaps because, as a species,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 665752.0,
      "end_time": 670360.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve been used to that sound every morning for millions of years."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 670360.0,
      "end_time": 677839.0,
      "text": "(Birds chirp)"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 677839.0,
      "end_time": 681504.0,
      "text": "On the other hand, industrial sounds have been introduced to us"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 681504.0,
      "end_time": 683969.0,
      "text": "a little more recently."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 683969.0,
      "end_time": 686051.0,
      "text": "Even though I really like them personally --"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 686051.0,
      "end_time": 688488.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve been used by one of my heroes, David Lynch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 688488.0,
      "end_time": 690447.0,
      "text": "and his sound designer, Alan Splet --"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 690447.0,
      "end_time": 693033.0,
      "text": "industrial sounds often carry negative connotations."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 693033.0,
      "end_time": 700092.0,
      "text": "(Machine noises)"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 700092.0,
      "end_time": 706869.0,
      "text": "Now, sound effects can tap into our emotional memory."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 706869.0,
      "end_time": 709250.0,
      "text": "Occasionally, they can be so significant"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 709250.0,
      "end_time": 712569.0,
      "text": "that they become a character in a movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 712569.0,
      "end_time": 718373.0,
      "text": "The sound of thunder may indicate divine intervention or anger."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 718373.0,
      "end_time": 723957.0,
      "text": "(Thunder)"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 723957.0,
      "end_time": 727956.0,
      "text": "Church bells can remind us of the passing of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 727956.0,
      "end_time": 731827.0,
      "text": "or perhaps our own mortality."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 731827.0,
      "end_time": 739773.0,
      "text": "(Bells ring)"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 739773.0,
      "end_time": 744287.0,
      "text": "And breaking of glass can indicate the end of a relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 744287.0,
      "end_time": 746390.0,
      "text": "or a friendship."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 746390.0,
      "end_time": 748788.0,
      "text": "(Glass breaks)"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 748788.0,
      "end_time": 752365.0,
      "text": "Scientists believe that dissonant sounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 752365.0,
      "end_time": 758438.0,
      "text": "for example, brass or wind instruments played very loud,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 758438.0,
      "end_time": 762906.0,
      "text": "may remind us of animal howls in nature"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 762906.0,
      "end_time": 766506.0,
      "text": "and therefore create a sense of irritation or fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 766506.0,
      "end_time": 772714.0,
      "text": "(Brass and wind instruments play)"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 772714.0,
      "end_time": 776298.0,
      "text": "So now we&#39;ve spoken about on-screen sounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 776298.0,
      "end_time": 780955.0,
      "text": "But occasionally, the source of a sound cannot be seen."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 780955.0,
      "end_time": 783503.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what we call offscreen sounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 783503.0,
      "end_time": 785641.0,
      "text": "or &quot;acousmatic.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 785641.0,
      "end_time": 787887.0,
      "text": "Acousmatic sounds --"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 787887.0,
      "end_time": 792944.0,
      "text": "well, the term &quot;acousmatic&quot; comes from Pythagoras in ancient Greece,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 792944.0,
      "end_time": 796559.0,
      "text": "who used to teach behind a veil or curtain for years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 796559.0,
      "end_time": 799773.0,
      "text": "not revealing himself to his disciples."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 799773.0,
      "end_time": 803727.0,
      "text": "I think the mathematician and philosopher thought that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 803727.0,
      "end_time": 805584.0,
      "text": "in that way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 805584.0,
      "end_time": 809645.0,
      "text": "his students might focus more on the voice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 809645.0,
      "end_time": 811633.0,
      "text": "and his words and its meaning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 811633.0,
      "end_time": 814827.0,
      "text": "rather than the visual of him speaking."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 814827.0,
      "end_time": 817550.0,
      "text": "So sort of like the Wizard of Oz,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 817550.0,
      "end_time": 822388.0,
      "text": "or &quot;1984&#39;s&quot; Big Brother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 822388.0,
      "end_time": 825678.0,
      "text": "separating the voice from its source,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 825678.0,
      "end_time": 828379.0,
      "text": "separating cause and effect"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 828379.0,
      "end_time": 832198.0,
      "text": "sort of creates a sense of ubiquity or panopticism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 832198.0,
      "end_time": 835156.0,
      "text": "and therefore, authority."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 835156.0,
      "end_time": 839129.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a strong tradition of acousmatic sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 839129.0,
      "end_time": 845763.0,
      "text": "Nuns in monasteries in Rome and Venice used to sing in rooms"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 845763.0,
      "end_time": 849646.0,
      "text": "up in galleries close to the ceiling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 849646.0,
      "end_time": 854390.0,
      "text": "creating the illusion that we&#39;re listening to angels up in the sky."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 854390.0,
      "end_time": 858104.0,
      "text": "Richard Wagner famously created the hidden orchestra"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 858104.0,
      "end_time": 861964.0,
      "text": "that was placed in a pit between the stage and the audience."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 861964.0,
      "end_time": 867420.0,
      "text": "And one of my heroes, Aphex Twin, famously hid in dark corners of clubs."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 867420.0,
      "end_time": 872187.0,
      "text": "I think what all these masters knew is that by hiding the source,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 872187.0,
      "end_time": 873874.0,
      "text": "you create a sense of mystery."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 873874.0,
      "end_time": 875967.0,
      "text": "This has been seen in cinema over and over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 875967.0,
      "end_time": 879071.0,
      "text": "with Hitchcock, and Ridley Scott in &quot;Alien.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 879071.0,
      "end_time": 881487.0,
      "text": "Hearing a sound without knowing its source"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 881487.0,
      "end_time": 886530.0,
      "text": "is going to create some sort of tension."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 886530.0,
      "end_time": 892168.0,
      "text": "Also, it can minimize certain visual restrictions that directors have"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 892168.0,
      "end_time": 895882.0,
      "text": "and can show something that wasn&#39;t there during filming."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 895882.0,
      "end_time": 897991.0,
      "text": "And if all this sounds a little theoretical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 897991.0,
      "end_time": 901289.0,
      "text": "I wanted to play a little video."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 901289.0,
      "end_time": 904383.0,
      "text": "(Toy squeaks)"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 904383.0,
      "end_time": 907761.0,
      "text": "(Typewriter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 907761.0,
      "end_time": 911164.0,
      "text": "(Drums)"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 911164.0,
      "end_time": 914484.0,
      "text": "(Ping-pong)"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 914484.0,
      "end_time": 917786.0,
      "text": "(Knives being sharpened)"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 917786.0,
      "end_time": 921405.0,
      "text": "(Record scratches)"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 921405.0,
      "end_time": 922615.0,
      "text": "(Saw cuts)"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 922615.0,
      "end_time": 924663.0,
      "text": "(Woman screams)"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 924663.0,
      "end_time": 929930.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;m sort of trying to demonstrate with these tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 929930.0,
      "end_time": 932516.0,
      "text": "is that sound is a language."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 932516.0,
      "end_time": 936571.0,
      "text": "It can trick us by transporting us geographically;"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 936571.0,
      "end_time": 938579.0,
      "text": "it can change the mood;"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 938579.0,
      "end_time": 941482.0,
      "text": "it can set the pace;"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 941482.0,
      "end_time": 946698.0,
      "text": "it can make us laugh or it can make us scared."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 946698.0,
      "end_time": 950072.0,
      "text": "On a personal level, I fell in love with that language"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 950072.0,
      "end_time": 951413.0,
      "text": "a few years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 951413.0,
      "end_time": 957274.0,
      "text": "and somehow managed to make it into some sort of profession."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 957274.0,
      "end_time": 960524.0,
      "text": "And I think with our work through the sound library,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 960524.0,
      "end_time": 967797.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re trying to kind of expand the vocabulary of that language."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 967797.0,
      "end_time": 971303.0,
      "text": "And in that way, we want to offer the right tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 971303.0,
      "end_time": 972967.0,
      "text": "to sound designers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 972967.0,
      "end_time": 974339.0,
      "text": "filmmakers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 974339.0,
      "end_time": 976748.0,
      "text": "and video game and app designers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 976748.0,
      "end_time": 980382.0,
      "text": "to keep telling even better stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 980382.0,
      "end_time": 983138.0,
      "text": "and creating even more beautiful lies."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 983138.0,
      "end_time": 984449.0,
      "text": "So thanks for listening."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 984449.0,
      "end_time": 994449.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
